metadata.name: Respire
metadata.description:
In a world where gravity's grip is loosened, we're reminded of the fundamental rhythm of our existence - our breath. 

This connection, so often forgotten in the hustle of life above, gains new importance here in the depths. Every inhalation, a gift of life; every exhalation, a surrender to the journey ahead. 

In this silent ballet beneath the waves, our breath becomes our guide, setting the tempo for our aquatic odyssey.
